YAIbot

Yet Another IRC bot, is based on the well known Bot::BasicBot::Pluggable
framework that allows this bot to have very interesting features like
on the fly modules load, in this way your bot can continue to have new
features without the need to reload the bot everytime you want to add
a new feature to it.

